Manyan ra'ayoyi uku na farko sun kasance kafin fitina (fyaucewa yana faruwa kafin ƙunci), tsakiyar ƙunci (fyaucewa yana faruwa a kusa ko kusa da tsakiyar lokacin ƙunci), da kuma bayan fitina (fyaucewa na faruwa a ƙarshen ƙunci).
Ra'ayi na huɗu, wanda aka fi sani da pre-fushin, shine ɗan ƙaramin gyare-gyare na matsakaicin matsin lamba.
Na farko, yana da mahimmanci a fahimci dalilin tsananin.
